name: Alissa Lynn Hollander
text: I ordered the Chicken Artichoke and Bacon Pizza with thick crust at my neighborhood Papa Murphy's. It was so convenient and the pizza was delicious!

name: L.K. H.
text: Wow! Great customer service. Beautiful pizza with lots of toppings. Great price with my coupon. Fast, friendly. Perfect end to a rough day.

name: Nico Laca
text: Went into this store for the first time the other day and was greeted by a young man by the name of Ian, he was very educated on the menu and pricing and made my visit excellent, great store here in Scottsdale.
